tellraw @a {"text": "Troubled, are you?", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Blocked by the sealed walls.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Well, shortly after the second reaping began, this very merchant ship sailed down the underground river.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "It was caught on the fringes of the temporal warp that immersed this accursed land.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "When they reached the famed Sea Gate, the occupants were all slaughtered.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "All but one, that is.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "He survived and met a man with whom you are acquainted: The Last King of Tyre.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "From there, he followed in your footsteps.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Or rather, you followed his.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "But he met a few unlike yourself, turned about, and went to make his amends.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Subjectivity, brave one.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "His amends are not yours.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "Follow him all the way to the deepest part of the cavern beneath New Hoiro.", "color": "white", "italic": true}
tellraw @a {"text": "There, you may break the seal.", "color": "white", "italic": true}